1
00:00:02,796 --> 00:00:04,616
This is taking forever.

2
00:00:05,044 --> 00:00:07,280
How long does a person need?

3
00:00:09,526 --> 00:00:09,900
Hey.

4
00:00:10,777 --> 00:00:12,145
What took you so long?

5
00:00:13,246 --> 00:00:16,416
I was getting your graduation gift.

6
00:00:17,584 --> 00:00:18,218
Here.

7
00:00:19,152 --> 00:00:21,955
I thought we were making them together.

8
00:00:21,955 --> 00:00:22,956
Why'd you go and do it yourself?

9
00:00:23,223 --> 00:00:24,491
I wanted to surprise you.

10
00:00:26,192 --> 00:00:27,260
Where's the other one?

11
00:00:27,827 --> 00:00:28,995
I know there's more than one.

12
00:00:29,996 --> 00:00:30,830
Where?

13
00:00:33,133 --> 00:00:34,567
Gotcha!

14
00:00:36,569 --> 00:00:38,631
You have [part of the character
of] "right" in your name, I do too.

15
00:00:39,472 --> 00:00:40,774
We'll both wear them on our right.

16
00:00:41,141 --> 00:00:42,108
See?

17
00:00:42,108 --> 00:00:42,876
Once we start college,

18
00:00:42,876 --> 00:00:44,677
I can keep a close eye on you.

19
00:00:46,292 --> 00:00:46,893
Wait.

20
00:00:48,782 --> 00:00:50,016
Is this going to hold you back?

21
00:00:51,017 --> 00:00:51,751
Hold you back from what?

22
00:00:52,886 --> 00:00:53,720
You know...

23
00:00:54,354 --> 00:00:56,022
Everyone says it's because of me

24
00:00:56,022 --> 00:00:57,557
that you don't have a girlfriend.

25
00:00:58,258 --> 00:00:59,926
Little do they know, for three years,

26
00:00:59,926 --> 00:01:01,594
I've been your human shield.

27
00:01:01,594 --> 00:01:03,563
I've taken all the hits for you.

28
00:01:05,131 --> 00:01:06,933
Then I'll just have to give myself to you.

29
00:01:08,201 --> 00:01:09,436
No thanks, someone else can have you.

30
00:01:09,736 --> 00:01:10,770
You're so big,

31
00:01:11,171 --> 00:01:12,038
just keeping you fed

32
00:01:12,038 --> 00:01:13,706
would cost a fortune.

33
00:01:17,010 --> 00:01:17,811
Fine.

34
00:01:18,111 --> 00:01:20,246
Since you got me a gift,

35
00:01:21,114 --> 00:01:21,981
and to celebrate us

36
00:01:21,981 --> 00:01:23,550
getting into the same college...

37
00:01:24,617 --> 00:01:26,553
Tonight is my treat.

38
00:01:31,257 --> 00:01:33,526
Did you get taller again?

39
00:01:36,963 --> 00:01:38,231
What do you want? You pick.

40
00:01:38,231 --> 00:01:38,898
Come on.

41
00:01:39,399 --> 00:01:40,066
What are you in the mood for?

42
00:01:40,066 --> 00:01:41,668
You still haven't said what you want.

43
00:01:42,402 --> 00:01:44,209
Careful, I'm gonna fall!

44
00:01:46,239 --> 00:01:48,074
I'm so stuffed.

45
00:01:50,643 --> 00:01:51,744
I'm the one who's stuffed.

46
00:01:51,744 --> 00:01:53,346
I had to finish everything you didn't.

47
00:01:55,348 --> 00:01:56,216
Hey...

48
00:01:56,716 --> 00:01:58,017
Do you think we'll always be like this?

49
00:01:59,285 --> 00:02:00,753
Unless you get sick of me.

50
00:02:02,188 --> 00:02:03,556
How could I ever get sick of you?

51
00:02:04,190 --> 00:02:05,024
Who knows?

52
00:02:05,024 --> 00:02:06,826
Once you get a girlfriend in college,

53
00:02:07,227 --> 00:02:08,728
you'll be the one sick of me.

54
00:02:12,699 --> 00:02:14,100
I'm not planning on getting a girlfriend.

55
00:02:16,803 --> 00:02:18,204
So you're staying with me forever?
